snippet.title: A Walk in the Dark - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
A Walk in the Dark is now available for Xbox One and PC!

You can purchase the game here:
http://a-walk-in-the-dark.com/

http://store.steampowered.com/app/248730/

https://www.microsoft.com/store/apps/9p1vgzdd6m16

Like us on facebook and receive all news and updates first hand:
http://www.facebook.com/AWalkInTheDark

Original Soundtrack:
http://codycook.bandcamp.com/album/a-walk-in-the-dark

http://itunes.apple.com/us/album/a-walk-in-the-dark/id494049932
